<p>And indeed, once again, greetings unto you, beloved and holy friends. We
come forth to abide with you because you have asked. We come forth to
abide with you because we are a part of you. We exist where you are. We
abide as the Truth of what you are.</p>

<p>Therefore, beloved friends, please well understand that when we reach
back into time, into the field of what you call <em>physicality</em> to create a
