only place that genuine communication can occur‚Äì<em>in Reality</em>.</p>

<p>This can only mean that in those moments when you <em>feel</em>‚Äìnot merely
intellectually consider‚Äìbut when you <em>feel</em> yourself immediately and
truly comprehending that which is communicated, or mediated by the words
